_inner-container\">\n<h3>Climbing to the top of Yapahuwa Rock Fortress<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The top of the staircase is not yet the final point of the rock fortress. A 20-minute climb via a steep, tricky but doable walking path gets you to the summit where you will be rewarded with a 360-degree view of the entire region! <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Read: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/sri-lanka-route-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Ultimate 3-week Sri Lanka Route Guide<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113224\/Yapahuwa-Rock-Fortress-sri-lanka-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"36197\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113224\/Yapahuwa-Rock-Fortress-sri-lanka.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=36197\" class=\"wp-image-36197 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113224\/Yapahuwa-Rock-Fortress-sri-lanka-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113224\/Yapahuwa-Rock-Fortress-sri-lanka-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2